OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy in
OL,6,Fthe northwest, perhaps with some
OL,7,Fpatchy rain for Northern Ireland and
OL,8,Fwestern Scotland. Largely clear and
OL,9,Fdry elsewhere but staying very warm
OL,10,Fand muggy overnight for parts of
OL,11,FWales, western and southern England.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FRain and thundery showers
OL,14,Fover northwest Scotland turning heavy
OL,15,Fat times. Low cloud and fog possibly
OL,16,Faffecting North Sea coasts. Otherwise,
OL,17,Fwidely very hot and humid day with
OL,18,Fstrong sunshine.
